# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# IMPORTANT THINGS WE DELIBERATELY DO NOT IGNORE
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# - All hand-written C++ source (*.cpp, *.hpp, *.h, *.c, *.cc, etc.)
# - compile_commands.json → many teams now TRACK this (for clangd, etc.)
#   → if you want it tracked, remove the line above or use:
#   !compile_commands.json   # at the end of the file
# - Cargo.lock → track in libraries, ignore in apps
# - pnpm-lock.yaml / package-lock.json → usually tracked now

# Recommended final override (uncomment if you want clangd/ccls to work out-of-the-box):
# !build/compile_commands.json
# !compile_commands.json
